係貼近啲既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中後期都睇左好多次"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T18:00:43.000Z","msg":"IS係咪講緊葦月伊織個套?<br />\n費事搞錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T18:02:33.000Z","msg":"係呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T18:06:27.000Z","msg":"完整好多,不過其實都係男主同女主不斷放閃<br />\n中間真係冇咩局外人插到手<br />\n係學妹搞下事咁樣(我其實覺得學妹好撚正)<br />\n成套野都係講佢兩個主線,都冇咩其他支線<br />\n睇完會有一種好甜既感覺<br />\n<br />\n草莓就中間好亂,亂戰咁款<br />\n記得個陣睇網上係嘈到痴撚左線,最後其實無論邊個贏都會有其他支持者出黎屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我覺得西野係正確選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00a683a9e6181a0745371546eb23db7b8908cbb4","tid":2298223,"uid":372029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"625f63872f9b186c2fbef89e51f2fca59660eadb","tid":2298223,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T17:47:45.000Z","msg":"一定係西野，東城係後傳比第二條仔追走左，正臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T19:24:27.000Z","msg":"後傳垃撚圾 出幾集就畀人斬咗<br />\n利申冇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/mouse_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0767374b50639831c1b9d83f89646f592e6b29dd","tid":2298223,"uid":98223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T19:55:32.000Z","msg":"一定係北大路<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"855915b6d7b0b035141164c2456a25940f344b72","tid":2298223,"uid":11055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T19:57:59.000Z","msg":"西軍"},{"pid":"ec9adf4812c621e517974cd11a301f24189ffa51","tid":2298223,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"138943f48b6fbe14820d8e946dcf30e2a9983ab6","tid":2298223,"uid":77205,"like":0,"dislike